name: ice cream #8 [SPECIAL EDITION - PINK FLOYD]
description: inspired by the legendary musical album cover - The Dark Side of the Moon - by Pink Floyd, an English rock band formed in London in 1964, one of the first British psychedelic groups. They became a leading band of the progressive rock genre, cited by some as the greatest progressive rock band of all time. This ice cream is made by glass material, any lights that comes through it will be dispersed become a beautiful rainbow.
